# Steps to install SASS

1. Created the directory 0x03-sass_scss inside the alx-intermediate-frontend repository:
   $ mkdir 0x03-sass_scss

2. Installed Node Version Manager (nvm):
   $ curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.39.7/install.sh | bash

3. Exited and reopened the terminal.

4. Installed Node.js version 20.16:
   $ nvm install 20.16

5. Verified Node and npm installation:
   $ node -v
   $ npm -v

6. Installed SASS version 3.7.4 using npm:
   $ npm install sass -v 3.7.4

7. Verified SASS installation:
   $ npx sass --version
